The paper deals with algorithmic problems related to searching for substrings in a sequence, which is a classic problem in computer science. The use case for this problem is in biological applications, which suggests that the paper may belong to the cs.BIO sub-category. However, the paper focuses on developing algorithms and improving upon previous results, which suggests that it may also belong to the cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), or cs.CG (Computational Geometry) sub-categories.
